flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: New product introduction or update to product attributes (packaging, composition, country of origin) or scheduled reclassification run.]
  A --> N1[Stream: STREAMS (ETL) - Inbound product update detected (new SKU or attribute change)]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Process Builder - Rules node - Enrich attributes and apply deterministic mapping rules]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Remote Functions (tariff API lookup) - Validate candidate HS code against authoritative tariff reference}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions (S4 writeback) + Process Builder Transaction - Writeback or escalate]
  N4 --> N5[PB: CWB Lifecycle (Action Item) + UI Screen - Human review for exceptions]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Process Builder - Notification / UI Screen (report) - Notify stakeholders and surface results]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Products in the product master have authoritative HS codes with an auditable decision trail; majority of SKUs classified automatically; ambiguous or high-risk cases routed to customs for human review; S4 updated with accepted classifications.]
  N3 -->|Multiple HS codes match with similar ...| B1[Create a CWB exception, include candidate codes, supporting attributes and historical mappings; route to customs/compliance team for adjudication.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Classification remains pending until human reviewer selects HS code; decision recorded and written back to S4 after approval.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Authoritative tariff API unavailable ...| B2[Fallback to local mapping table (ruleset) and mark classification as 'validated locally' with elevated audit risk; schedule retry and flag for post-check.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: HS code written to S4 with audit note and follow-up task for reconciliation once API is available.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Insufficient product attribute data f...| B3[Block automatic writeback, generate information request Action Item to product owner (via CWB/UI Screen), and hold SKU in 'classification pending' status.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: No HS code assigned until required attributes are supplied; process tracks time-to-resolution and escalates if SLA missed.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]